Interlock areas are now restricted.

28
00:04:17,863 --> 00:04:20,406
You pulled us off the power grid,
Philippe.

29
00:04:20,616 --> 00:04:23,243
Because you're scaring the hell
out of everyone.

30
00:04:23,410 --> 00:04:26,956
The collider was never intended
to generate antimatter.

31
00:04:27,165 --> 00:04:30,501
All three canisters are stored
under every possible safeguard.

32
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:33,212
I'm only asking you to wait.

33
00:04:33,547 --> 00:04:37,591
We can't wait. The bulk of the
antimatter is generated at start-up.

34
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:39,093
Put us back online.

35
00:04:39,803 --> 00:04:42,930
Do you want to call the director,
or shall I?

36
00:04:43,098 --> 00:04:46,684
ATLAS underground
is now in restricted mode.

37
00:04:46,893 --> 00:04:48,310
Vittoria, Vittoria.

38
00:04:48,478 --> 00:04:50,146
Protons are being loaded.

39
00:04:50,438 --> 00:04:52,982
Don't blow us all to heaven.

40
00:04:53,150 --> 00:04:54,316
Please.

41
00:04:54,484 --> 00:04:57,445
Powering on LHC magnets.

42
00:04:58,697 --> 00:05:02,325
lon source stage
in four three, two.

43
00:05:02,493 --> 00:05:04,202
We are powering up. Here we go.

44
00:05:04,370 --> 00:05:06,246
Start the collision sequence.

45
00:05:06,414 --> 00:05:09,249
Vittoria what did Philippe want?

46
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:13,837
They're terrified. He wants us to wait.
What do you think?

47
00:05:14,172 --> 00:05:19,342
I think if we don't harvest now,
we never will.

48
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:22,095
Beam-on-beam stability is good.
Take your places, people.

49
00:05:22,263 --> 00:05:24,139
ATLAS at CMS check.

50
00:05:24,307 --> 00:05:28,143
Sending timing trigger now.
Collisions imminent.

51
00:05:28,978 --> 00:05:31,688
We have got 10 to the 13th protons
per bunch.

52
00:05:32,648 --> 00:05:35,358
Let's hope the heavy ion guys
didn't mess up.

53
00:05:35,526 --> 00:05:38,528
Beams at relativistic velocities.

54
00:05:39,615 --> 00:05:42,158
Luminosity monitors operational.

55
00:05:42,326 --> 00:05:44,535
Beamline has no restrictions.

56
00:05:44,703 --> 00:05:46,496
Enable beam capture.

57
00:05:46,663 --> 00:05:48,873
Accelerating the beam.

58
00:05:49,041 --> 00:05:50,875
Stage one, line up.

59
00:05:51,043 --> 00:05:52,668
Magnets to full field.

60
00:05:52,836 --> 00:05:54,462
Load functions to magnets.

61
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:56,547
