743
01:02:27,488 --> 01:02:29,156
In case you're not aware of it...

744
01:02:29,324 --> 01:02:32,701
papal autopsy is prohibited
by Vatican law.

745
01:02:32,869 --> 01:02:35,120
We're not going to defile
His Holiness's body

746
01:02:35,288 --> 01:02:36,914
just because his enemies claim...

747
01:02:37,081 --> 01:02:40,125
- Why would they send this letter now?
- Well, to cause panic.

748
01:02:40,293 --> 01:02:42,628
"The sun will blind at midnight

749
01:02:42,795 --> 01:02:45,422
and neither police nor professors
can stop it."

750
01:02:46,174 --> 01:02:47,549
He knows I'm here.

751
01:02:47,717 --> 01:02:50,552
Obviously they were hoping
this letter would become public.

752
01:02:50,720 --> 01:02:52,721
We might be wise to preempt
their attempt

753
01:02:52,889 --> 01:02:56,016
by making an announcement
of our own to refute this absurd claim.

754
01:02:56,184 --> 01:02:57,726
That's out of the question.

755
01:02:57,894 --> 01:03:01,022
Cardinal Strauss has insisted
this entire matter be kept internal.

756
01:03:01,190 --> 01:03:03,358
He shouldn't be aware of it.
He's in conclave.

757
01:03:03,525 --> 01:03:07,445
His final instructions before sealing
the doors were very clear.

758
01:03:07,613 --> 01:03:10,657
Cardinal Strauss does not dictate
Vatican protocols.

759
01:03:11,367 --> 01:03:13,284
As you say, yet, technically

760
01:03:13,452 --> 01:03:14,994
now that conclave has begun...

761
01:03:15,162 --> 01:03:18,206
It's his privilege and duty
to control public announcements.

762
01:03:18,374 --> 01:03:21,042
I've drafted a release
about the incident in the piazza

763
01:03:21,210 --> 01:03:24,712
but any other statements
are specifically prohibited.

764
01:03:24,880 --> 01:03:29,717
For that, Cardinal has asked me
to remind you we have a chimney.

765
01:03:33,722 --> 01:03:36,224
Commander Richter,
the search for the device?

766
01:03:36,392 --> 01:03:40,271
Well, we've turned the power on and
oft to about 20 percent of Vatican City.

767
01:03:40,438 --> 01:03:43,065
- Nothing on the video yet.
- We're running out of options.

768
01:03:43,233 --> 01:03:45,067
How long would you need
to evacuate?

769
01:03:45,235 --> 01:03:48,404
If I pull all my men from the search
for the bomb, 30 minutes.

770
01:03:50,156 --> 01:03:54,535
Mr. Langdon. You have been right
so far about the path. It's now 9:15.

771
01:03:54,703 --> 01:03:56,662
How quickly can you find
the next church?

772
01:03:56,830 --> 01:03:59,748
The lines on the carving pointed east,
away from Vatican City.

773
01:03:59,916 --> 01:04:02,751
But there were five of them,
so there's room for error.

774
01:04:02,919 --> 01:04:05,254
About 20 churches intersect
those lines.

775
01:04:05,422 --> 01:04:07,423
None of them have names
that invoke fire.

776
01:04:07,591 --> 01:04:10,384
So a Bernini sculpture must be inside
one of them that does.

777
01:04:10,552 --> 01:04:12,678
We'll need to get
into the archives to find it.

778
01:04:12,846 --> 01:04:15,682
- Would you escort Mr. Langdon?
- Yes, Father.

779
01:04:17,894 --> 01:04:19,269
Silvano's journals.

780
01:04:19,437 --> 01:04:22,105
The killer's name could be in here.
May I stay?

781
01:04:22,607 --> 01:04:24,274
Please. Fine, of course.

782
01:04:25,902 --> 01:04:27,777
Professor.

783
01:04:28,613 --> 01:04:31,948
Would it surprise you to find
those clothes suit you?

784
01:04:32,617 --> 01:04:34,951
It would surprise the hell out of me.

785
01:04:49,880 --> 01:04:55,010
The Vatican is expressing sympathy
for the mugging victim

786
01:04:55,177 --> 01:04:59,472
a Dusseldorf tourist,
now confirmed dead.

787
01:04:59,640 --> 01:05:04,102
The Vatican police have a suspect
in custody.

788
01:05:04,270 --> 01:05:11,276
The Vatican will allow the crowd back
into St. Peter's Square

789
01:05:11,444 --> 01:05:13,153
where security will be doubled.

790
01:05:13,320 --> 01:05:17,574
The Vatican did admit that where there
are crowds, so often follows crime.

791
01:05:17,742 --> 01:05:20,493
We're trying now to get the name
of the tourist who was...

792
01:05:20,661 --> 01:05:23,330
- Oh, wait.
- Hand to the right. Keep panning.

793
01:05:23,497 --> 01:05:25,415
We're getting word now of smoke.

794
01:05:25,583 --> 01:05:27,876
Smoke from
the Sistine Chapel chimney.

795
01:05:28,044 --> 01:05:30,295
Apparently there's been
another vote.

796
01:05:30,463 --> 01:05:32,130
The smoke is black.

797
01:05:32,298 --> 01:05:35,008
Once again, the cardinals have failed
to reach consensus

798
01:05:35,176 --> 01:05:37,761
and the Catholic Church
remains without a leader.

799
01:05:46,395 --> 01:05:48,313
What are you looking for now?

800
01:05:49,273 --> 01:05:50,857
Church assets.

801
01:05:51,025 --> 01:05:52,567
I beg your pardon?

802
01:05:52,735 --> 01:05:54,652
Artwork. It's valuable.

803
01:05:54,820 --> 01:05:57,989
Corporations tend to keep track
of their holdings.

804
01:05:58,157 --> 01:06:01,785
The Catholic Church
is not a corporation, it's a beacon.

805
01:06:02,495 --> 01:06:05,580
A source of inspiration for one billion
lost and frightened souls.

806
01:06:05,748 --> 01:06:08,416
Sure, I get that. It's also a bank.

807
01:06:19,178 --> 01:06:22,681
Commander Olivetti said I was not
to leave your side this time.

808
01:06:25,059 --> 01:06:26,267
It wasn't me, it was her.

809
01:07:25,036 --> 01:07:26,953
Power is now cut to Zone 73.

810
01:07:27,121 --> 01:07:29,456
No light reaction on the monitor.

811
01:07:29,623 --> 01:07:33,126
Restore power and move on to 74.

812
01:07:43,637 --> 01:07:44,929
What sort of signs?

813
01:07:46,640 --> 01:07:48,016
I'm sorry?

814
01:07:51,687 --> 01:07:56,232
If the Holy Father was given
an overdose of Tinzaparin

815
01:07:56,442 --> 01:07:58,443
what signs would his body bear?

816
01:08:00,363 --> 01:08:02,238
Bleeding of the oral mucosa.

817
01:08:03,741 --> 01:08:04,866
His tongue.

818
01:08:05,034 --> 01:08:09,162
Postmortem, the blood congeals and
turns the inside of the mouth black.

819
01:08:11,582 --> 01:08:13,500
Even after 14 days?

820
01:08:13,668 --> 01:08:16,586
It wouldn't show up
until at least a week after his death.

821
01:08:21,842 --> 01:08:23,760
He was very important to me.

822
01:08:25,513 --> 01:08:27,597
Yeah, I understand.

823
01:08:32,853 --> 01:08:35,021
Will you come with me, please?

824
01:08:42,071 --> 01:08:44,197
Signore, would you organize
a security team

825
01:08:44,365 --> 01:08:46,783
to escort Miss Vetra and myself
down to the crypt?

826
01:08:46,993 --> 01:08:49,244
- Yes, sir.
- We'll be leaving straightaway.

827
01:09:08,556 --> 01:09:09,806
Do you smoke?

828
01:09:11,809 --> 01:09:13,768
A little bit.

829
01:09:13,936 --> 01:09:16,563
Then you better sit down
before you keel over.

830
01:09:18,899 --> 01:09:21,317
And what's all that right there?

831
01:09:22,903 --> 01:09:25,238
What does this say
in Italian right here

832
01:09:25,406 --> 01:09:27,824
next to the Ecstasy of Saint Teresa?
Right there.

833
01:09:30,828 --> 01:09:33,038
"Moved at suggestion of the artist."

834
01:09:34,165 --> 01:09:37,667
"Moved"? To another church.
At the suggestion of Bernini?

835
01:09:38,336 --> 01:09:39,836
I don't know.

836
01:09:41,547 --> 01:09:44,424
Here. Translate all of this for me

837
01:09:44,592 --> 01:09:46,593
and I'll buy you a pack of smokes.

838
01:09:46,761 --> 01:09:48,595
I'm looking for a reference to fire.

839
01:09:48,763 --> 01:09:50,347
Fires.

840
01:09:51,849 --> 01:09:55,560
- "Seraphim,", meaning "the fiery one."
- Right.

841
01:09:56,687 --> 01:10:00,940
"His great, golden spear,
a point of fire."

842
01:10:02,860 --> 01:10:06,780
Then "woman left completely afire."

843
01:10:06,947 --> 01:10:10,950
Ecstasy of Saint Teresa.
Saint Teresa on fire.

844
01:10:11,118 --> 01:10:14,079
So this sculpture
was moved to this church?

845
01:10:15,665 --> 01:10:19,125
Why did they shut down the system?
They know we're down here.

846
01:10:19,293 --> 01:10:23,213
If there's no power,
there's no oxygen.

847
01:10:23,381 --> 01:10:26,383
- Can we get out?
- The door is electronic.

848
01:10:27,635 --> 01:10:29,469
Oh, God.

849
01:10:29,637 --> 01:10:31,388
Well, that's disappointing.

850
01:10:33,182 --> 01:10:34,391
Where are we going?

851
01:10:34,600 --> 01:10:36,559
To see my father.

852
01:10:36,727 --> 01:10:38,144
I don't understand.

853
01:10:38,312 --> 01:10:42,232
I was orphaned when I was 9 years
of age. A bombing in Ulster.

854
01:10:42,400 --> 01:10:45,694
The UVF protesting the visit
of a Catholic archbishop.

855
01:10:45,861 --> 01:10:50,532
The archbishop felt responsible,
and he adopted me the following day.

856
01:10:50,700 --> 01:10:53,827
I was raised by him
and by the Church.

857
01:10:54,120 --> 01:10:56,538
He was the wisest man I ever met.

858
01:10:56,706 --> 01:11:00,500
Even when I was young and stubborn,
I wanted to be ordained.

859
01:11:00,668 --> 01:11:04,170
But I was brought up in Italy, so I
also wanted to do my military service.

860
01:11:04,338 --> 01:11:05,922
I wanted to fight.

861
01:11:06,632 --> 01:11:09,759
He told me, "Learn to fly."

862
01:11:09,927 --> 01:11:12,178
So I joined
the Aeronautica Militare...

863
01:11:12,346 --> 01:11:16,099
flew helicopters,
bringing the wounded back to hospital.

864
01:11:16,267 --> 01:11:17,434
He was a great man.

865
01:11:17,643 --> 01:11:19,686
Your father died?

866
01:11:20,646 --> 01:11:22,272
Fourteen days ago.

867
01:11:23,566 --> 01:11:25,567
Command, do you read me?

868
01:11:25,735 --> 01:11:28,445
Power is off. Oxygen is very low.

869
01:11:28,654 --> 01:11:30,780
Come in. Can you read me?

870
01:11:30,948 --> 01:11:32,032
Can you get anything?

871
01:11:32,199 --> 01:11:36,453
No. The walls are lead-lined.
There's no signal.

872
01:14:59,115 --> 01:15:00,490
This way.

873
01:15:09,000 --> 01:15:13,003
If the Holy Father was murdered,
the implications are profound.

874
01:15:13,629 --> 01:15:15,755
Vatican security is impenetrable.

875
01:15:15,923 --> 01:15:18,842
No one from the outside
could have got anywhere near him.

876
01:15:19,010 --> 01:15:20,635
It was someone on the inside.

877
01:15:20,803 --> 01:15:23,596
And we can trust no one.

878
01:15:25,391 --> 01:15:28,435
No light reaction on Zone 97.

879
01:15:28,936 --> 01:15:32,856
Based on the rate the battery
is using power

880
01:15:33,024 --> 01:15:36,109
the device will detonate
just before midnight.

881
01:15:58,049 --> 01:16:00,050
Holy Father...

882
01:16:00,801 --> 01:16:04,429
when I was young, you told me
the voice in my heart was God's voice.

883
01:16:05,222 --> 01:16:08,141
You said I should follow it,
no matter how painful.

884
01:16:08,309 --> 01:16:10,060
Forgive me.

885
01:16:10,311 --> 01:16:11,686
Please.

886
01:16:11,896 --> 01:16:13,605
Give me strength.

887
01:16:14,940 --> 01:16:19,903
What I do, I do in the name
of everything you believe.

888
01:16:30,623 --> 01:16:32,082
Remove the cover.

889
01:16:35,419 --> 01:16:37,212
Did you not hear me?

890
01:16:37,546 --> 01:16:40,548
Signore by law,
we are at you command, but...

891
01:16:40,758 --> 01:16:44,094
One day I will ask your forgiveness for
putting you in this position.

892
01:16:44,303 --> 01:16:46,096
But today I ask your obedience.

893
01:16:48,057 --> 01:16:50,725
Vatican laws are there
to protect this church.

894
01:16:50,893 --> 01:16:55,063
And it's in that spirit that I command
you to break one of them now.

895
01:17:50,578 --> 01:17:52,245
God help us.

896
01:18:05,217 --> 01:18:08,178
Santa Maria della Vittoria.
Do you know it?

897
01:18:08,346 --> 01:18:11,598
- Yes, I do.
- It's the next church.

898
01:18:27,782 --> 01:18:29,741
I think someone just tried to kill me.

899
01:18:29,909 --> 01:18:32,243
- I promise you we had no idea...
- He knows I'm here.

900
01:18:32,411 --> 01:18:33,995
- Yes.
- You heard me ask permission.

901
01:18:34,205 --> 01:18:36,122
- You gave me an escort.
- We had no idea

902
01:18:36,290 --> 01:18:40,460
that portions of our white zones
were cross-wired with that building.

903
01:18:40,628 --> 01:18:42,587
Commander Richter
was extending the search.

904
01:18:42,755 --> 01:18:46,216
If he had known,
he never would have killed the power.

905
01:18:47,259 --> 01:18:49,511
Or there is the other possibility.

906
01:18:49,720 --> 01:18:52,222
Is it conceivable the Illuminati

907
01:18:53,349 --> 01:18:55,225
have infiltrated the Swiss Guard?

908
01:18:58,521 --> 01:19:00,021
Perhaps.

909
01:19:05,528 --> 01:19:10,073
- I wanna speak to the camerlengo.
- The camerlengo is unavailable.

910
01:19:10,282 --> 01:19:13,952
He's found evidence that the
Holy Father was indeed murdered.

911
01:19:15,371 --> 01:19:17,706
- He is seeking guidance.
- From whom?

912
01:19:18,666 --> 01:19:20,417
From God.

913
01:19:20,751 --> 01:19:22,460
- Make an effort. Please.
- Yeah, yeah.

914
01:19:55,578 --> 01:19:56,911
The journals. Where are they?

915
01:19:59,915 --> 01:20:02,167
Who took the journals
from this desk?

916
01:20:10,301 --> 01:20:12,385
Someone is here? What is this?

917
01:20:12,553 --> 01:20:15,263
Signore, this is unacceptable.

918
01:20:15,848 --> 01:20:19,184
For a camerlengo to enter the chapel
once conclave has begun.

919
01:20:19,352 --> 01:20:22,604
Forgive me.
There's been a development.

920
01:20:33,115 --> 01:20:35,784
His Holiness Celestine V
was murdered.

921
01:20:35,951 --> 01:20:39,621
Is it so hard to believe
it could happen again?

922
01:20:39,914 --> 01:20:42,082
Signori, please, a moment.

923
01:20:42,249 --> 01:20:44,834
Please, signori.

924
01:20:46,212 --> 01:20:48,797
Our Church is at war.

925
01:20:49,882 --> 01:20:53,343
We are under attack
from an old enemy.

926
01:20:53,511 --> 01:20:54,886
The Illuminati.

927
01:20:55,930 --> 01:20:57,639
They have struck us from within.

928
01:20:58,140 --> 01:21:00,266
Murdering our Holy Father.

929
01:21:00,726 --> 01:21:05,397
And threatening us all with destruction
at the hands of their new god, science.

930
01:21:05,564 --> 01:21:08,775
They call it retribution.
They think it justified.

931
01:21:08,943 --> 01:21:11,820
Because of the Church's attacks
on men of science in the past.

932
01:21:11,987 --> 01:21:13,655
And it's true.

933
01:21:14,281 --> 01:21:15,573
Since the days of Galileo

934
01:21:15,741 --> 01:21:19,494
this Church has tried to slow
the relentless march of progress

935
01:21:19,662 --> 01:21:21,955
sometimes with misguided means.

936
01:21:23,416 --> 01:21:27,085
But science and religion
are not enemies.

937
01:21:27,253 --> 01:21:28,920
There are simply some things

938
01:21:29,088 --> 01:21:32,173
that science is just too young
to understand.

939
01:21:32,341 --> 01:21:37,429
So the Church pleads,
"Stop. Slow down. Think. Wait."

940
01:21:37,930 --> 01:21:40,682
And for this they call us backward.

941
01:21:40,850 --> 01:21:43,018
But who is more ignorant...

942
01:21:43,269 --> 01:21:45,437
the man
who cannot define lightning

943
01:21:45,604 --> 01:21:49,524
or the man who does not respect
its natural awesome power?

944
01:21:50,151 --> 01:21:52,694
The battle is well underway, signori.

945
01:21:53,362 --> 01:21:55,071
We must defend ourselves.

946
01:21:55,239 --> 01:21:58,241
But what if this time we fight
their stealth with openness?

947
01:21:58,409 --> 01:22:01,036
Combat their wicked scheme
with simple truth

948
01:22:01,203 --> 01:22:04,247
and end this brutish battle
once and for all.

949
01:22:06,834 --> 01:22:13,340
We must open the doors, tear down the
blacken curtains and speak to our flock.

950
01:22:13,507 --> 01:22:16,426
If the outside world could see
this Church as I do

951
01:22:16,594 --> 01:22:18,762
looking beyond the ritual
of these walls

952
01:22:18,929 --> 01:22:22,432
they would see a modern miracle.

953
01:22:22,600 --> 01:22:25,602
A brotherhood of imperfect,
simple souls

954
01:22:25,770 --> 01:22:28,480
who want nothing more
than to be voices of compassion

955
01:22:28,647 --> 01:22:32,025
in a world spinning out of control.

956
01:22:33,152 --> 01:22:36,654
Signori I ask

957
01:22:37,615 --> 01:22:39,658
I pray

958
01:22:39,825 --> 01:22:42,160
that you break this conclave.

959
01:22:43,037 --> 01:22:45,413
Open the doors

960
01:22:45,581 --> 01:22:47,832
evacuate St. Peter's Square...

961
01:22:48,042 --> 01:22:50,960
and tell the world the truth.

962
01:23:24,662 --> 01:23:26,538
Oh, my God.

963
01:23:26,706 --> 01:23:28,623
Get him down!

964
01:23:29,834 --> 01:23:31,626
No!

965
01:23:40,803 --> 01:23:42,679
There, there, that chain.
On that pulley.

966
01:23:42,847 --> 01:23:44,645
This bench. Get this pew up here.
Make a ladder.

967
01:26:52,328 --> 01:26:53,411
My son

968
01:26:55,164 --> 01:26:57,874
God answers all prayers,

969
01:26:59,168 --> 01:27:01,002
but sometimes his answer is no.

970
01:27:03,214 --> 01:27:05,840
The College will not break conclave.

971
01:27:07,134 --> 01:27:08,468
May I suggest

972
01:27:09,303 --> 01:27:10,679
you direct your energies

973
01:27:10,846 --> 01:27:14,516
to helping the Swiss Guard find
this explosive device

974
01:27:15,184 --> 01:27:16,851
if it exists.

975
01:27:18,145 --> 01:27:19,688
And leave Church leadership

976
01:27:22,274 --> 01:27:23,858
to its leaders.

977
01:27:37,039 --> 01:27:38,206
Eminence.

978
01:27:40,876 --> 01:27:45,213
There is a growing fear
that without the four preferiti

979
01:27:45,798 --> 01:27:50,969
a two-thirds majority
for any candidate will not be possible.

980
01:27:51,137 --> 01:27:53,972
- Unless...
- Speak plainly.

981
01:27:55,057 --> 01:27:56,683
It is the recommendation of many

982
01:27:56,851 --> 01:28:00,478
that you ask to be removed
from your post as Great Elector

983
01:28:01,522 --> 01:28:05,108
thereby making yourself eligible

984
01:28:05,276 --> 01:28:08,403
to wear the Ring of the Fisherman.

985
01:28:09,572 --> 01:28:11,406
Well

986
01:28:11,574 --> 01:28:13,867
if it is God's will

987
01:28:21,125 --> 01:28:22,876
may his will be done.

988
01:28:51,280 --> 01:28:53,615
Signore, are you okay?

989
01:29:18,599 --> 01:29:21,476
Those journals are private property.
I demand you return them.

990
01:29:21,644 --> 01:29:25,230
They're material evidence
in a Vatican investigation.

991
01:29:27,233 --> 01:29:29,442
I am an Italian citizen.
My rights do not end

992
01:29:29,610 --> 01:29:32,404
- just because I crossed to the other...
- This is not Italy.

993
01:29:32,571 --> 01:29:34,614
It's not even Rome,
it's the Vatican.

994
01:29:34,782 --> 01:29:36,574
A country of its own
with its own laws.

995
01:29:36,742 --> 01:29:40,078
And when those journals passed
the border, they became my property.

996
01:29:40,246 --> 01:29:42,080
I will give them back to you

997
01:29:42,248 --> 01:29:45,583
when I've decided they contain
nothing of value to the investigation.

998
01:29:45,751 --> 01:29:48,878
Do you have something to hide,
Comandante Richter?

999
01:29:51,382 --> 01:29:53,675
Do you, Dr. Vetra?

1000
01:30:15,531 --> 01:30:18,491
Were it up to me,
it would not be this way.

1001
01:30:19,910 --> 01:30:22,579
It's a sin to kill with pain.

1002
01:30:23,706 --> 01:30:25,540
It's a sin to kill without reason.

1003
01:30:29,420 --> 01:30:30,962
Father...

1004
01:30:32,590 --> 01:30:33,965
they make me a sinner.

1005
01:31:13,756 --> 01:31:16,341
Saint Teresa on fire.

1006
01:31:19,428 --> 01:31:21,096
Professor Langdon?

1007
01:31:22,306 --> 01:31:24,224
- What direction is that?
- West, I think.

1008
01:31:24,392 --> 01:31:27,227
"Cross Rome
the mystic elements unfold."

1009
01:31:28,646 --> 01:31:30,939
Piazza Barberini is here.

1010
01:31:31,107 --> 01:31:34,109
Saint Teresa is here.

1011
01:31:34,694 --> 01:31:36,820
Where is the Santa Maria
del Popolo?

1012
01:31:36,987 --> 01:31:39,614
- Santa Maria del Popolo?
- Yes.

1013
01:31:40,700 --> 01:31:42,200
Thank you.

1014
01:31:42,910 --> 01:31:45,036
St. Peter's is here.

1015
01:31:45,204 --> 01:31:47,330
We are here.

1016
01:31:48,874 --> 01:31:50,417
A church with water.

1017
01:31:52,753 --> 01:31:54,546
Wait, wait, wait.

1018
01:31:54,714 --> 01:31:56,381
"Cross Rome."

1019
01:31:58,509 --> 01:32:00,552
The poem must mean it literally,
cross Rome.

1020
01:32:00,720 --> 01:32:02,887
Professor, Commander Richter
has ordered me

1021
01:32:03,055 --> 01:32:04,764
to escort you
to the Vatican immediately.

1022
01:32:04,932 --> 01:32:06,099
Piazza Navona.

1023
01:32:06,267 --> 01:32:10,020
Earth. Air. Fire. Water.

1024
01:32:10,187 --> 01:32:12,147
Cross Rome.

1025
01:32:12,314 --> 01:32:14,482
Bernini's Four Rivers.

1026
01:32:15,192 --> 01:32:18,528
Professor Langdon, the Vatican insists
that I have to take you back immediately.

1027
01:32:18,696 --> 01:32:21,698
The Vatican is about to see
its fourth cardinal murdered tonight.

1028
01:32:21,866 --> 01:32:26,786
Now, look. You can do as they say
and force me back to the Vatican

1029
01:32:26,954 --> 01:32:28,997
where we can all mourn
his death together.

1030
01:32:29,165 --> 01:32:33,084
Or you can show how real cops act,
and take me to the Piazza Navona

1031
01:32:33,252 --> 01:32:36,463
where we still might be able
to stop it.

1032
01:32:39,425 --> 01:32:42,135
Oh, by all means, let's talk it over.

1033
01:32:42,303 --> 01:32:44,971
In 14 minutes, he's gonna be dead.

1034
01:32:50,895 --> 01:32:52,062
This way, professor.

1035
01:33:00,738 --> 01:33:02,489
Yes, Padre?

1036
01:33:02,698 --> 01:33:06,493
At 11:15,
if the Church is still in peril

1037
01:33:06,702 --> 01:33:09,579
give the order
to evacuate the cardinals.

1038
01:33:10,081 --> 01:33:12,165
But with dignity.

1039
01:33:12,333 --> 01:33:16,294
Let them walk out into St. Peter's
Square with their heads held high.

1040
01:33:16,462 --> 01:33:19,130
I don't want the last image
of this Church to be of men

1041
01:33:19,298 --> 01:33:21,466
sneaking out the back door.

1042
01:33:38,567 --> 01:33:40,610
"Let angels guide thee."

1043
01:33:45,992 --> 01:33:47,534
There it is.

1044
01:33:47,743 --> 01:33:49,869
- There it is.
- Professor, I know this fountain.

1045
01:33:50,037 --> 01:33:53,540
- There is no angel on it.
- The dove. The Angel of Peace.

1046
01:33:53,749 --> 01:33:56,042
And it's looking in what direction?

1047
01:33:56,252 --> 01:33:57,961
East, I think.

1048
01:34:09,390 --> 01:34:10,682
Professor, just wait here.

1049
01:34:11,350 --> 01:34:13,101
Stay put.

1050
01:34:49,722 --> 01:34:51,806
Good evening. Can you help me?

1051
01:34:52,224 --> 01:34:54,434
I'm waiting for a doctor.

1052
01:35:10,910 --> 01:35:12,619
Come here.

1053
01:35:15,498 --> 01:35:18,124
Stay calm. Don't shoot.

1054
01:35:55,454 --> 01:35:56,538
Hey!

1055
01:36:11,387 --> 01:36:12,804
Help!

1056
01:36:12,972 --> 01:36:14,014
Somebody help!

1057
01:36:53,387 --> 01:36:55,096
Help, somebody!

1058
01:38:09,171 --> 01:38:10,755
Cardinal Baggia?

1059
01:38:10,923 --> 01:38:12,173
Cardinal Baggia.

1060
01:38:14,468 --> 01:38:16,469
Where was he hiding you?

1061
01:38:16,637 --> 01:38:18,763
The Church of Illumination,
where is it?

1062
01:38:19,390 --> 01:38:22,684
Castel... Castel Sant'Angelo.

1063
01:38:24,186 --> 01:38:25,603
Castle of the Angel.

1064
01:38:48,586 --> 01:38:51,546
Sir, there's news
about Cardinal Baggia.

1065
01:38:52,089 --> 01:38:55,633
The cardinal told Langdon he was
being held in Castel Sant'Angelo.

1066
01:38:55,801 --> 01:38:58,720
If Langdon's right,
that's where the bomb is.

1067
01:38:58,888 --> 01:39:00,638
Send everyone we can spare.

1068
01:39:00,806 --> 01:39:01,973
And you?

1069
01:39:02,141 --> 01:39:03,850
I'm staying here.

1070
01:39:17,198 --> 01:39:18,740
Vittoria.

1071
01:39:19,575 --> 01:39:21,076
- You're all right.
- I'm all right.

1072
01:39:21,243 --> 01:39:22,827
What about you? I just heard.

1073
01:39:22,995 --> 01:39:24,371
I'm all right, I'm okay.

1074
01:39:30,628 --> 01:39:33,922
Robert, we can't trust Richter.
He took Silvano's journals.

1075
01:39:34,090 --> 01:39:36,800
There must be something in there
he doesn't want us to see.

1076
01:39:36,967 --> 01:39:38,760
The head of the Swiss Guard.

1077
01:39:40,179 --> 01:39:43,264
Castel Sant'Angelo, it's close enough,
so the signal from that camera

1078
01:39:43,432 --> 01:39:45,183
could still reach the Vatican.

1079
01:39:47,103 --> 01:39:49,938
The Church of Illumination
is somewhere here.

1080
01:39:50,106 --> 01:39:52,399
Your canister is inside it.

1081
01:40:12,753 --> 01:40:14,212
Come with me.

1082
01:40:18,134 --> 01:40:21,761
For 400 years, the Illuminati
met right under the Church's nose.

1083
01:40:21,929 --> 01:40:25,390
The Vatican used this as a hideout
and as a prison for their enemies.

1084
01:40:25,558 --> 01:40:30,437
If the explosion happens here, would
the blast radius take out the Vatican?

1085
01:40:30,604 --> 01:40:32,647
And part of Rome along with it.

1086
01:40:34,692 --> 01:40:36,067
Go on.

1087
01:40:51,000 --> 01:40:52,834
They're pointing to it.
The angels.

1088
01:40:53,002 --> 01:40:54,961
The canister must be down there.
Come on.

1089
01:41:43,344 --> 01:41:45,679
- Where are they going?
- To search the outer castle.

1090
01:41:45,846 --> 01:41:48,181
No, no. It has to be here!

1091
01:41:53,229 --> 01:41:55,021
Robert, it's a dead end.

1092
01:41:55,189 --> 01:41:57,232
No, it's not.

1093
01:41:57,400 --> 01:41:59,776
See if you can find a flashlight.

1094
01:42:16,711 --> 01:42:19,129
All of these stones
are rectangular granite.

1095
01:42:19,296 --> 01:42:22,382
Except right here. What is this?

1096
01:42:26,095 --> 01:42:27,303
It's a pentagram.

1097
01:42:27,722 --> 01:42:28,805
An eye

1098
01:42:29,515 --> 01:42:31,099
that leads to.

1099
01:42:31,267 --> 01:42:32,767
Nowhere.

1100
01:42:41,944 --> 01:42:43,194
Robert?

1101
01:42:45,114 --> 01:42:47,615
These walls overlap
and there's a passageway back here.

1102
01:42:47,783 --> 01:42:49,326
Here, let me have the flashlight.

1103
01:43:13,142 --> 01:43:16,269
It's a passageway
that leads to the Vatican.

1104
01:43:16,437 --> 01:43:17,979
An ancient escape route.

1105
01:43:20,816 --> 01:43:21,858
My God.

1106
01:43:24,820 --> 01:43:26,154
Here.

1107
01:43:28,407 --> 01:43:30,325
Look.

1108
01:43:52,056 --> 01:43:54,557
This would be the perfect place
for the Illuminati to blow...

1109
01:43:54,725 --> 01:43:55,767
the whole building up.

1110
01:43:55,935 --> 01:43:57,977
Here. Here.

1111
01:44:03,025 --> 01:44:07,028
Get on the radio. Get the word out.
Conclave remains sealed.

1112
01:44:07,196 --> 01:44:09,656
But the camerlengo gave the order
for evacuation at...

1113
01:44:09,824 --> 01:44:11,616
I'm countermanding it.

1114
01:44:17,206 --> 01:44:19,332
This is it. This is their church.

1115
01:44:21,711 --> 01:44:24,713
The canister should be lit
by artificial light.

1116
01:44:48,487 --> 01:44:49,654
It's not here, Robert.

1117
01:44:49,822 --> 01:44:52,615
"A shining star at the end of the path."
It has to be.

1118
01:44:52,783 --> 01:44:54,659
It's not here.

1119
01:44:54,827 --> 01:44:56,828
- What did the poem say?
- Nothing.

1120
01:44:56,996 --> 01:45:01,916
Nothing, it's all over. It was just the
four lines, each one describing the.

1121
01:45:11,510 --> 01:45:12,761
There's a fifth brand.

1122
01:45:13,429 --> 01:45:15,638
It's not an ambigram,
it's just two crossed keys.

1123
01:45:15,806 --> 01:45:18,600
- The symbol for the Vatican.
- No.

1124
01:45:19,435 --> 01:45:20,852
No, the papacy.

1125
01:45:21,020 --> 01:45:22,437
They intend to kill him.

1126
01:45:22,605 --> 01:45:25,231
Before they destroy the Vatican,
they're gonna kill

1127
01:45:25,399 --> 01:45:28,026
- and brand the pope himself.
- There is no pope.

1128
01:45:28,194 --> 01:45:29,819
Tempe sede vacante.

1129
01:45:29,987 --> 01:45:31,946
Il camerlengo.

1130
01:45:33,866 --> 01:45:36,618
- We have to warn him.
- Take a step back, please.

1131
01:45:37,745 --> 01:45:40,288
Take your cell phone
from your pocket.

1132
01:45:43,542 --> 01:45:45,043
Throw it in the fire.

1133
01:45:56,180 --> 01:45:57,597
Murderer.

1134
01:45:57,765 --> 01:46:00,308
You know, when they call me...

1135
01:46:00,559 --> 01:46:01,935
and they all call me

1136
01:46:02,561 --> 01:46:05,105
it is so important to them
that I know

1137
01:46:05,272 --> 01:46:07,982
that what they ask
is the Lord's will.

1138
01:46:08,150 --> 01:46:10,985
Or Allah's, or Yahweh's.

1139
01:46:12,405 --> 01:46:14,322
And I suppose they're right.

1140
01:46:18,703 --> 01:46:22,372
Because if he was not vengeful,
I would not exist, now would I?

1141
01:46:23,165 --> 01:46:25,750
I've had several chances
to eliminate you tonight.

1142
01:46:25,918 --> 01:46:28,128
You're still alive
because you have no weapon

1143
01:46:28,295 --> 01:46:31,381
and they didn't ask me to kill you,
but if you pursue me

1144
01:46:31,549 --> 01:46:33,675
it is another matter.

1145
01:46:40,391 --> 01:46:41,683
Be careful.

1146
01:46:42,268 --> 01:46:44,394
These are men of God.

1147
01:46:56,907 --> 01:46:58,658
The camerlengo.

1148
01:47:19,263 --> 01:47:21,556
- Camerlengo will grant you audience.
- Good.

1149
01:47:21,932 --> 01:47:23,850
I'd like to see him alone.

1150
01:47:25,728 --> 01:47:28,897
That's impossible, sir.
No one sees the camerlengo alone.

1151
01:47:29,065 --> 01:47:31,274
Have you forgotten
who you're working for?

1152
01:47:33,069 --> 01:47:34,527
No, sir.

1153
01:47:59,011 --> 01:48:01,096
Have you come to make me a martyr?

1154
01:48:08,354 --> 01:48:10,939
Here. Here. Here.

1155
01:49:37,735 --> 01:49:40,111
- I need to see the camerlengo.
- He is not available.

1156
01:49:40,279 --> 01:49:43,198
- I demand to see the camerlengo!
- He is not available.

1157
01:49:43,991 --> 01:49:45,659
We'll see about that.

1158
01:49:55,086 --> 01:49:57,962
All locked up. Senza chiave,
it's a one-way portal.

1159
01:49:58,130 --> 01:50:00,382
The only entrance
is on the other side.

1160
01:50:00,549 --> 01:50:03,259
No! Hey!

1161
01:50:03,427 --> 01:50:08,640
I don't care who he talks to.
He doesn't go into that room.

1162
01:50:10,685 --> 01:50:13,853
This is Robert Langdon and Dr. Vetra!
Open the door!

1163
01:50:15,815 --> 01:50:16,981
Open up!

1164
01:50:20,861 --> 01:50:22,237
Open the door!

1165
01:50:22,446 --> 01:50:24,072
Hey!

1166
01:50:27,410 --> 01:50:29,411
The camerlengo is in danger.

1167
01:50:43,175 --> 01:50:45,010
He's the one!
He's got a gun!

1168
01:50:49,515 --> 01:50:51,224
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1169
01:50:51,392 --> 01:50:54,060
- Illuminatus!
- Sanctimonious bastard!

1170
01:51:03,696 --> 01:51:05,113
Order the evacuation.

1171
01:51:05,281 --> 01:51:07,073
We only have 19 minutes.

1172
01:51:11,412 --> 01:51:13,163
Here, he's...

1173
01:51:13,331 --> 01:51:15,332
Get the helicopter
for the older cardinals.

1174
01:51:15,499 --> 01:51:16,875
Yes, sir.

1175
01:51:29,889 --> 01:51:31,222
Robert?

1176
01:51:31,390 --> 01:51:34,684
The brand, the symbol,
could it have another meaning?

1177
01:51:40,691 --> 01:51:43,443
Crossed keys.
But those are upside down.

1178
01:51:44,070 --> 01:51:45,570
St. Peter.

1179
01:51:46,781 --> 01:51:48,531
The first pope

1180
01:51:49,408 --> 01:51:51,117
was crucified upside down.

1181
01:51:51,285 --> 01:51:53,828
- On Vatican Hill.
- A few hundred feet below us.

1182
01:51:53,996 --> 01:51:55,330
Necropolis, city of the dead.

1183
01:51:55,498 --> 01:51:57,916
"Upon this rock
I will build my church."

1184
01:51:58,084 --> 01:52:00,960
Or bring it down upon itself.

1185
01:52:01,837 --> 01:52:04,839
The bomb is in St. Peter's tomb.

1186
01:52:20,022 --> 01:52:21,523
The grid is still cycling.

1187
01:52:21,691 --> 01:52:24,067
The power to this section
must be down.

1188
01:53:22,376 --> 01:53:25,211
It must be here. It must be.

1189
01:53:36,724 --> 01:53:38,475
Don't touch it.

1190
01:53:39,602 --> 01:53:41,686
We have seven minutes.

1191
01:53:47,151 --> 01:53:49,486
Robert, hold this.

1192
01:54:30,569 --> 01:54:32,570
It's cold down here, isn't it?

1193
01:54:32,738 --> 01:54:34,072
What's wrong?

1194
01:54:34,657 --> 01:54:37,033
Cold decreases battery life.

1195
01:54:39,161 --> 01:54:40,996
We may have less than five minutes.

1196
01:54:41,664 --> 01:54:42,998
So?

1197
01:54:43,165 --> 01:54:45,750
If I pull the power
with less than five minutes

1198
01:54:45,918 --> 01:54:48,461
the residual charge
won't hold suspension.

1199
01:54:50,339 --> 01:54:53,299
We should leave it here
and get clear if we can.

1200
01:54:53,467 --> 01:54:55,677
- At least down here, the damage...
- No!

1201
01:54:55,845 --> 01:54:58,013
- No, wait!
- Father!

1202
01:55:00,433 --> 01:55:02,350
We are live here
at St. Peter's Square

1203
01:55:02,518 --> 01:55:06,021
where despite a bomb threat
and an order of evacuation

1204
01:55:06,188 --> 01:55:09,774
the crowd is actually growing
in size as we await an official...

1205
01:55:09,942 --> 01:55:11,860
announcement
from the Vatican spokesman

1206
01:55:12,028 --> 01:55:14,029
as to the exact nature
of the threat

1207
01:55:14,196 --> 01:55:17,782
and whether or not they
are treating it as a credible danger.

1208
01:55:25,416 --> 01:55:26,624
This way.

1209
01:55:59,450 --> 01:56:01,368
A bomb?

1210
01:56:06,082 --> 01:56:09,918
Roberto, there's an emergency.
I'll take her up alone.

1211
01:56:14,006 --> 01:56:15,757
He's got clearance.

1212
01:56:40,992 --> 01:56:42,909
Oh, my God.

1213
01:58:44,448 --> 01:58:45,824
Get down!

1214
02:01:38,622 --> 02:01:40,707
Cardinal Strauss?

1215
02:01:41,000 --> 02:01:44,919
It was the camerlengo.
He saved us all!

1216
02:01:45,087 --> 02:01:49,049
He saved the church and he is alive.

1217
02:01:50,009 --> 02:01:51,593
Praise God. Praise God.

1218
02:01:57,350 --> 02:01:58,767
He is alive.

1219
02:01:58,934 --> 02:02:02,437
He sacrificed himself for all of us.

1220
02:02:09,445 --> 02:02:11,654
It's so incredible. He survived.

1221
02:02:30,508 --> 02:02:34,469
You know, the worst thing
we thought would happen

1222
02:02:34,637 --> 02:02:38,640
was that our work would fall into
the hands of the energy companies.

1223
02:02:40,851 --> 02:02:43,144
We thought
we could change the world.

1224
02:02:43,688 --> 02:02:44,896
So naive.

1225
02:02:45,064 --> 02:02:48,692
No, no. Not naive.

1226
02:02:48,859 --> 02:02:50,694
Innocent, maybe.

1227
02:02:50,861 --> 02:02:53,154
But that's not a crime.

1228
02:02:54,532 --> 02:02:56,658
I'm not so sure.

1229
02:02:58,244 --> 02:03:00,745
Go back to work.

1230
02:03:01,664 --> 02:03:03,748
Change the world.

1231
02:03:22,685 --> 02:03:25,729
A gift. Do you understand
what I'm saying?

1232
02:03:25,896 --> 02:03:28,732
For Catholics, for everyone.

1233
02:03:28,899 --> 02:03:32,485
Camerlengo's age
shouldn't be an obstacle.

1234
02:03:32,653 --> 02:03:34,863
Signori,
you are no doubt aware

1235
02:03:35,031 --> 02:03:38,700
that by holy law the man is ineligible
for election to the papacy.

1236
02:03:38,868 --> 02:03:40,744
He is not a cardinal, he is a priest.

1237
02:03:40,911 --> 02:03:42,620
He is of insufficient age.

1238
02:03:42,788 --> 02:03:45,915
Well, maybe there's a way
we could consider the possibilities.

1239
02:03:46,083 --> 02:03:50,712
I am sorry. The protocols of conclave
are not subject to modification.

1240
02:03:50,880 --> 02:03:52,797
I will not call a ballot on this matter.

1241
02:03:52,965 --> 02:03:55,800
But, signore
you would not call the ballot.

1242
02:03:55,968 --> 02:03:57,260
Surely you remember.

1243
02:03:57,428 --> 02:04:00,221
You gave up your post
as Great Elector.

1244
02:04:00,389 --> 02:04:02,557
They are singing
in St. Peter's Square.

1245
02:04:02,725 --> 02:04:05,435
And what happened here tonight
transcends our laws.

1246
02:04:05,603 --> 02:04:06,644
Does it?

1247
02:04:06,812 --> 02:04:09,939
Is it God's will
that we give ourselves over to frenzy?

1248
02:04:10,107 --> 02:04:11,733
Discard the rules of the Church?

1249
02:04:11,901 --> 02:04:14,486
Perhaps we need not discard them.

1250
02:04:15,279 --> 02:04:21,201
Signore, I am thinking now of Romano
Pontifici Eligendo, Numero Sessanta...

1251
02:04:21,369 --> 02:04:23,161
Acclamation by Adoration.

1252
02:04:24,580 --> 02:04:27,666
If the Holy Spirit speaks
through us

1253
02:04:27,833 --> 02:04:30,210
and we call a man's name
out loud...

1254
02:04:30,378 --> 02:04:33,004
That is election by adoration.

1255
02:04:33,172 --> 02:04:35,590
- He's God's choice.
- Yes.

1256
02:04:35,758 --> 02:04:40,762
And the candidate need only be
an ordained member of the clergy

1257
02:04:40,930 --> 02:04:45,642
present in the Sistine Chapel
at the moment of his election.

1258
02:04:53,693 --> 02:04:55,193
I think we have it settled.

1259
02:05:18,884 --> 02:05:20,093
Signore Camerlengo.

1260
02:05:20,720 --> 02:05:21,761
Yes?

1261
02:05:21,929 --> 02:05:25,974
The cardinals ask you to join them
in conclave as soon as possible.

1262
02:05:26,142 --> 02:05:27,350
Me?

1263
02:05:27,518 --> 02:05:29,602
Yes, Padre.

1264
02:05:52,168 --> 02:05:53,335
What are you doing?

1265
02:05:53,502 --> 02:05:56,588
Silvano's journals.
I want them back.

1266
02:06:21,030 --> 02:06:23,031
Richter said

1267
02:06:24,200 --> 02:06:26,201
His Holiness suffered
from seizures...

1268
02:06:26,369 --> 02:06:28,703
but steps were taken

1269
02:06:29,830 --> 02:06:31,498
for safety.

1270
02:06:35,878 --> 02:06:38,880
"Made sure he was watched,"
he said.

1271
02:06:40,383 --> 02:06:44,052
What if he was trying
to give me this key?

1272
02:06:44,720 --> 02:06:47,097
That's the papal office.

1273
02:06:47,264 --> 02:06:49,140
If the pope was worried
about seizures

1274
02:06:49,308 --> 02:06:52,394
he must have had Richter
install cameras without telling anyone.

1275
02:06:52,561 --> 02:06:55,230
To keep an eye on him. For safety.

1276
02:06:57,066 --> 02:06:58,817
Maybe it records.

1277
02:07:09,829 --> 02:07:11,538
I read the journals, Patrick.

1278
02:07:11,706 --> 02:07:14,290
The scientist kept journals. So?

1279
02:07:14,458 --> 02:07:16,167
Well you figure prominently
in them.

1280
02:07:16,877 --> 02:07:17,919
Really?

1281
02:07:18,087 --> 02:07:22,507
Bentivoglio wasn't just a physicist,
he was also a Catholic priest.

1282
02:07:23,092 --> 02:07:27,095
And as such, he was deeply conflicted
about the implications of his work

1283
02:07:27,263 --> 02:07:29,764
and in need of spiritual guidance.

1284
02:07:29,932 --> 02:07:31,766
Like Galileo.

1285
02:07:32,727 --> 02:07:35,979
About a month ago, he requested
an audience with the pope,

1286
02:07:36,147 --> 02:07:37,856
but you know that.

1287
02:07:38,024 --> 02:07:41,276
Because you granted the audience,
and you were also present during it.

1288
02:07:41,444 --> 02:07:44,446
The God particle.
To actually claim an act of creation.

1289
02:07:44,613 --> 02:07:46,448
The blasphemy. The arrogance.

1290
02:07:46,615 --> 02:07:49,200
The Holy Father didn't see it
like that.

1291
02:07:49,368 --> 02:07:51,286
He urged him to go public.

1292
02:07:51,454 --> 02:07:53,371
His Holiness
thought that the discovery...

1293
02:07:53,539 --> 02:07:57,584
could actually scientifically prove
the existence of a divine power

1294
02:07:57,752 --> 02:08:00,754
and begin to bridge the gap
between science and religion.

1295
02:08:00,921 --> 02:08:03,631
His work was not religious,
it was sacrilegious.

1296
02:08:03,799 --> 02:08:08,678
But you saw the pope's position
as a softening of Church law.

1297
02:08:09,472 --> 02:08:13,099
As an old man's weakness.
Your father's weakness.

1298
02:08:13,768 --> 02:08:15,435
You murdered the Vicar of Christ.

1299
02:08:15,603 --> 02:08:19,481
He raised me to protect this Church,
even from within.

1300
02:08:19,648 --> 02:08:23,651
And then you conjured up
an old enemy from the past.

1301
02:08:23,819 --> 02:08:25,653
The Illuminati.

1302
02:08:25,821 --> 02:08:29,949
You found the ancient brands in the
papal vaults, and put them to use.

1303
02:08:30,117 --> 02:08:31,159
To spread fear.

1304
02:08:31,327 --> 02:08:33,745
The cardinals are men of belief.

1305
02:08:33,913 --> 02:08:37,415
Right now, their belief in evil
is uniting them.

1306
02:08:37,583 --> 02:08:40,752
The entire Catholic world
will be united by this attack.

1307
02:08:40,920 --> 02:08:42,837
There is no attack.

1308
02:08:43,839 --> 02:08:46,633
You're trying to convince the cardinals
they're in a war

1309
02:08:46,801 --> 02:08:48,885
so they will choose a warrior
to lead them.

1310
02:08:49,053 --> 02:08:50,178
We are at war.

1311
02:08:50,346 --> 02:08:52,305
We're weak
when we should be strong.

1312
02:08:52,473 --> 02:08:56,309
If science is allowed
to claim the power of creation

1313
02:08:56,477 --> 02:08:58,186
what is left for God?

1314
02:08:58,354 --> 02:09:00,021
It didn't work, Patrick.

1315
02:09:01,524 --> 02:09:04,901
- It isn't finished.
- Oh, yes, it's finished.

1316
02:09:06,112 --> 02:09:08,029
It's finished.

1317
02:09:09,031 --> 02:09:11,866
I've shown the journals
to Father Simeon.

1318
02:09:12,034 --> 02:09:14,327
The moment the doors
to the conclave open

1319
02:09:14,495 --> 02:09:17,414
he will tell the cardinals
what you've done.

1320
02:09:17,957 --> 02:09:20,458
I was planning on doing this alone.

1321
02:09:23,379 --> 02:09:24,796
Put it down.

1322
02:09:27,466 --> 02:09:30,218
But perhaps it's better
that you're here.

1323
02:09:30,386 --> 02:09:31,511
Put it down.

1324
02:09:33,347 --> 02:09:35,140
Put it away.

1325
02:09:47,486 --> 02:09:50,488
Help! He's the one!
He's got a gun!

1326
02:09:54,327 --> 02:09:56,578
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1327
02:09:56,746 --> 02:09:59,289
- Illuminatus!
- Sanctimonious bastard!

1328
02:10:14,680 --> 02:10:17,682
And get the helicopter
for the older cardinals, right?

1329
02:10:21,270 --> 02:10:22,437
Robert?

1330
02:10:22,605 --> 02:10:25,357
The brand, the symbol,
could it have another meaning?

1331
02:11:08,943 --> 02:11:11,903
I've been summoned by
the College of Cardinals.

1332
02:12:25,353 --> 02:12:26,644
Gently

1333
02:12:26,812 --> 02:12:28,313
but within our walls.

1334
02:13:32,044 --> 02:13:35,755
Father, into thy hands
I commend my spirit.

1335
02:14:29,477 --> 02:14:31,144
Church sources now confirm...

1336
02:14:31,312 --> 02:14:33,563
that Camerlengo
Father Patrick McKenna

1337
02:14:33,731 --> 02:14:38,526
has died of internal injuries
sustained in his heroic fall.

1338
02:14:38,694 --> 02:14:40,820
Crowds of the faithful are calling for

1339
02:14:40,988 --> 02:14:44,991
the camerlengo's immediate
canonization and sainthood.

1340
02:14:45,159 --> 02:14:48,828
The Vatican also announced
the death of three of its cardinals

1341
02:14:48,996 --> 02:14:51,498
in the fire
at Santa Maria della Vittoria.

1342
02:14:51,666 --> 02:14:54,167
As we await the appearance
of the new Holy Father

1343
02:14:54,335 --> 02:14:55,960
Cardinal Baggia of Italy

1344
02:14:56,128 --> 02:14:59,714
one of the four original preferiti,
who, despite terrorist attempts

1345
02:14:59,882 --> 02:15:02,050
at disruption,
seems to have been selected

1346
02:15:02,218 --> 02:15:04,636
in one of the swiftest
and smoothest conclaves

1347
02:15:04,804 --> 02:15:06,596
in modern Church history.

1348
02:15:13,562 --> 02:15:15,480
Professor Langdon? Please.

1349
02:15:32,915 --> 02:15:36,251
A token of thanks
from His Holiness

1350
02:15:36,419 --> 02:15:39,504
and from his new camerlengo.

1351
02:15:40,756 --> 02:15:43,550
We are grateful you saved his life.

1352
02:15:43,718 --> 02:15:46,970
And it's our understanding
that you require this text

1353
02:15:47,138 --> 02:15:49,180
to complete your scholarly work.

1354
02:15:51,225 --> 02:15:54,352
We ask only that
in your last will and testament

1355
02:15:54,520 --> 02:15:56,813
you ensure,

1356
02:15:56,981 --> 02:15:58,898
it finds its way home.

1357
02:16:01,652 --> 02:16:02,736
Of course.

1358
02:16:02,903 --> 02:16:05,113
And when you write of us

1359
02:16:05,281 --> 02:16:08,074
and you will write of us

1360
02:16:08,242 --> 02:16:10,535
may I ask one thing?

1361
02:16:10,703 --> 02:16:12,287
Do so gently.

1362
02:16:14,790 --> 02:16:16,291
I'll try.

1363
02:16:16,459 --> 02:16:18,293
Religion is flawed,

1364
02:16:18,961 --> 02:16:21,796
but only because man is flawed.

1365
02:16:21,964 --> 02:16:25,383
All men, including this one.

1366
02:16:39,982 --> 02:16:41,816
He chose the name Luke.

1367
02:16:44,779 --> 02:16:47,489
There's been many Marks
and Johns...

1368
02:16:49,158 --> 02:16:50,742
never a Luke.

1369
02:16:51,452 --> 02:16:52,827
It's said he was a doctor.

1370
02:16:54,163 --> 02:16:58,166
It's quite a message,
science and faith all in one.

1371
02:16:58,334 --> 02:16:59,959
The world is in need of both.

1372
02:17:02,838 --> 02:17:05,256
You will counsel him wisely.

1373
02:17:05,591 --> 02:17:09,177
I am an old man.
I will counsel him briefly.

1374
02:17:14,809 --> 02:17:16,851
Mr. Langdon,

1375
02:17:22,024 --> 02:17:26,653
thanks be to God for sending
someone to protect his Church.

1376
02:17:30,866 --> 02:17:33,535
I don't believe
he sent me, Father.

1377
02:17:33,703 --> 02:17:35,996
Oh my son.

1378
02:17:36,163 --> 02:17:38,206
Of course he did.


